            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a polar region off-grid type wind-hydrogen energy supply system and a control method thereof, and relates to the field of new energy energy supply. A wind power system in the system converts wind energy into electric energy and charges a low-temperature battery energy storage system; the hydrogen fuel cell system is used for chemically converting hydrogen and oxygen into electric energy and charging the low-temperature battery energy storage system; the low-temperature battery energy storage system stores energy, stabilizes the volatility of wind power generation and smooths the load; the intelligent monitoring system obtains operation parameters of the wind power system, the low-temperature battery energy storage system and the hydrogen fuel cell system. Electric energy can be stably and efficiently output in extreme environments such as extremely cold, strong wind and snow and strong wind and sand, the use proportion of renewable energy sources is increased, and fuel consumption and emission of South Pole scientific investigation are reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种极地离网型风氢供能系统及其控制方法，涉及新能源供能领域。系统中风电系统将风能转换为电能，并向低温电池储能系统充电；氢燃料电池系统将氢气和氧气的化学转换成电能，并向低温电池储能系统充电；低温电池储能系统储能，平抑风力发电的波动性，平滑负荷；智能监控系统获取风电系统、低温电池储能系统和氢燃料电池系统的运行参数。本发明能够在面临极寒、强风雪、强风沙等极端环境下稳定高效的输出电能，提高可再生能源使用比例，减少南极科考燃料消耗和排放。"
                }
            ]
